      "description": "A map \u03c6:R\u2192S with \u03c6(a+b)=\u03c6(a)+\u03c6(b) and \u03c6(ab)=\u03c6(a)\u03c6(b). Preserves ring structure. ker(\u03c6) is an ideal; im(\u03c6) is a subring. Ring isomorphism: bijective ring homomorphism.",
